if exists (select 1
from sysindexes
where id = object_id('tblAdjustMachine')
and name = 'Index_StartDate_tblAdjustMachine'
and indid > 0
and indid < 255)
drop index tblAdjustMachine.Index_StartDate_tblAdjustMachine
go

if exists (select 1
from sysindexes
where id = object_id('tblAdjustMachine')
and name = 'Index_EndDate_tblAdjustMachine'
and indid > 0
and indid < 255)
drop index tblAdjustMachine.Index_EndDate_tblAdjustMachine
go

if exists (select 1
from sysindexes
where id = object_id('tblAdjustMachine')
and name = 'Index_DCCT_tblAdjuestMachine'
and indid > 0
and indid < 255)
drop index tblAdjustMachine.Index_DCCT_tblAdjuestMachine
go

if exists (select 1
from sysobjects
where id = object_id('tblAdjustMachine')
and type = 'U')
drop table tblAdjustMachine
go

/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: tblAdjustMachine */
/*==============================================================*/
create table tblAdjustMachine (
ID int null,
WorkOrderNo varchar(20) null,
ProductNo varchar(20) null,
ProductDesc varchar(50) null,
DispatchNo varchar(50) not null,
MachineNo varchar(50) null,
MouldNo varchar(50) null,
TotalQty int null,
StartDate datetime null,
EndDate datetime null,
AdjustMan varchar(20) not null,
Checker varchar(20) not null,
CheckDate datetime not null,
ModiHistoryContent varbinary(Max) null,
Remark varchar(200) null,
CardType int null,
constraint PK_TBLADJUSTMACHINE primary key nonclustered (DispatchNo, Checker, CheckDate)
)
go

declare @CurrentUser sysname
select @CurrentUser = user_name()
execute sp_addextendedproperty 'MS_Description',
'增加调机时的生产数据。',
'user', @CurrentUser, 'table', 'tblAdjustMachine'
go

/*==============================================================*/
/* Index: Index_DCCT_tblAdjuestMachine */
/*==============================================================*/
create clustered index Index_DCCT_tblAdjuestMachine on tblAdjustMachine (
DispatchNo ASC,
Checker ASC,
CardType ASC
)
go

/*==============================================================*/
/* Index: Index_EndDate_tblAdjustMachine */
/*==============================================================*/
create index Index_EndDate_tblAdjustMachine on tblAdjustMachine (
EndDate ASC
)
go

/*==============================================================*/
/* Index: Index_StartDate_tblAdjustMachine */
/*==============================================================*/
create index Index_StartDate_tblAdjustMachine on tblAdjustMachine (
StartDate ASC
)
go

from sysindexes
where id = object_id('tblAdjustMachine')

and indid > 0
and indid < 255)

/*==============================================================*/

DispatchNo ASC,
Checker ASC,
CardType ASC
)
go
